                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of g-C3N4/NiS/TiO2 ternary composite photocatalytic material",
                    "一种g-C3N4/NiS/TiO2三元复合光催化材料的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of a g-C3N4/NiS/TiO2 ternary composite photocatalytic material, and belongs to the technical field of preparation of photocatalytic materials. The technical problem that the photocatalytic hydrogen production performance is poor due to the fact that TiO2 is low in light utilization rate and high in photon-generated carrier recombination rate is solved. The g-C3N4/NiS/TiO2 ternary photocatalytic material is synthesized and prepared through a calcination method, a sol-gel method and an alcohol-thermal method, the structure of the g-C3N4/NiS/TiO2 ternary photocatalytic material is that a carbon nitride nanosheet is used as a substrate, spherical TiO2 is uniformly distributed on the substrate, and NiS nanoparticles are attached to TiO2. And if g-C3N4 is selected as a substrate, the specific surface area and the active sites can be increased. Light absorption is insufficient due to direct coupling, and the oxidation-reduction reaction rate is slow. By constructing an indirect Z-type heterostructure and through a cocatalyst NiS, the charge transfer capacity can be improved, and the photocatalyst has longer charge carrier life and better photocatalytic activity. According to the invention, a co-catalyst is loaded on a semiconductor, so that active sites can be enhanced, activation energy can be reduced, charge carriers can be captured, and recombination of photo-induced electrons and holes can be inhibited to promote oxidation-reduction reaction. NiS is a transition metal oxide and can replace an expensive noble metal cocatalyst. Meanwhile, NiS can also reduce the charge recombination rate of g-C3N4 and improve the catalytic activity. The prepared photocatalytic material is uniform in microstructure and has good photocatalytic hydrogen production activity, the hydrogen production amount within 4 hours is 45.49 mmoL/g, and the hydrogen production rate is 11.37 mmoL/g/h."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了g‑C3N4/NiS/TiO2三元复合光催化材料的制备方法，本发明属于光催化材料制备技术领域。本发明解决了TiO2对光利用率低，光生载流子复合速率快，导致光催化产氢性能差的技术问题。本发明通过煅烧法、溶胶‑凝胶法和醇热法合成制备了g‑C3N4/NiS/TiO2三元光催化材料，其结构为以氮化碳纳米片为基底，在上面均匀分布球状TiO2，在TiO2上附着NiS纳米颗粒。选取g‑C3N4作为基底的话，可以增加比表面积和增多活性位点。直接耦合会受到光吸收不足、氧化还原反应速率缓慢等问题。利用搭建间接的Z型异质结构，通过助催化剂NiS，可以提高电荷转移能力、而且具有更长的电荷载流子寿命以及更好的光催化活性。本发明是在半导体上负载助催化剂，可以增强活性位点，同时降低活化能、捕获电荷载流子和抑制光生电子和空穴的复合来促进氧化还原反应。NiS为过渡金属氧化物，可以代替价格比较昂贵的贵金属助催化剂。同时NiS也可以降低g‑C3N4的电荷复合率，提升催化活性。本发明制得的光催化材料微观结构均匀，具有良好的光催化产氢活性，4h的产氢量为45.49mmoL/g，产氢速率为11.37mmoL/g/h。"
                }
